        <li><strong>Play-Based Learning:</strong> We believe in learning through play, fostering creativity, curiosity, and social skills.</li>
        <li><strong>Holistic Development:</strong> Activities are tailored to support cognitive, emotional, physical, and spiritual growth.</li>
