    <div id="Frequently-Asked-Questions" class="content-section">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p>Find answers to common questions about our nursery program.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>What are the age requirements?</strong> Our nursery program is designed for children aged 2 to 4 years old.</li>
        <li><strong>What is the teacher-to-child ratio?</strong> We maintain a low ratio of 1:8 to ensure personalized attention and care.</li>
        <li><strong>What safety measures are in place?</strong> Our facilities are secure, with trained staff, regular safety drills, and strict health protocols.</li>
        <li><strong>How do you handle meals and allergies?</strong> We provide nutritious meals and accommodate dietary restrictions with care and communication.</li>
        <li><strong>Can parents visit the classroom?</strong> Yes, we encourage parent involvement and offer scheduled visits to observe and participate in activities.</li>
      </ul>
